      "context_id": "c",
      "signal_id": "d",
      "expected_hash_tag": "2mvp836a4"
    },
    {
      "_note": "separator-collision B：ctx 欄含 0x1e；byte-stream 與 A 相同 -> hash == A(兩側共有行為，非跨語言分歧；見報告 finding E4X-1)",
      "side_cell_key": "a",
      "context_id": "b\u001ec",
      "signal_id": "d",
      "expected_hash_tag": "2mvp836a4"
    },
    {
